Home And Away

Series Synopsis:
Home and Away is an Australian series that has been in production since January 1988. It was originally centered around Pippa and Tom Fletcher and the children that they foster, set in the small coastal fictional town, Summer Bay, just north of "The City," (Sydney).

Now, however, this classic Australian soap depicts the trials and tribulations, plus the romances, arguments, successes and failures of the people of this town.

Episode Synopsis:
Rachel confronts Tony about who he is secretly meeting. Aden is suspicious when Joey suddenly quits her job. Charlie's new found hope for romance doesn't last long.
